 This study does not support the role of D. rotundus as a reservoir of Bartonella species infecting livestock, which could be transmitted via bite and blood feeding and therefore suggest limited risk of zoonotic transmission of Bartonella from common vampire bats to humans.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Raya, Adam P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jaffe, David A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chomel, Bruno B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ota, Marissa S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tsou, Peter M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Davis, Aaron Z.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Olave-Leyva, Jos\u00e9 Ignacio", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Galvez-Romero, Guillermo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stuckey, Matthew J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kasten, Rickie W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Obreg\u00f3n-Morales, Cirani", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ar\u00e9chiga-Ceballos, Nidia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Martinez-Martinez, Flor", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aguilar-Seti\u00e9n, Alvaro", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/cdbda8cc7c86ab4a7ad1c31f7a520386", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/1916f721a67f42331503ed91f4cb547144d2c953c8752cb707253002981d029c", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/INTHDXWJ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/INTHDXWJ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/39ce960e3ce538e566447f24f4606736!/b58703-61254", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompile